        (111048, 'S.F.W.', 1994, 72125, 6, 42, 0, 0, 'An alienated and misanthropic teenager gains sudden and unwanted celebrity status after he''s taken hostage by terrorists where his indifference to their threats to kill him makes news headlines.', '/cBCUHXTzm2GSZ14FHfsJQgm4IDN.jpg', '/2o9zTDKdC4MHNIYBLgFMpO5ik9o.jpg', 0),
        (111070, 'The Santa Clause', 1994, 58072, 6, 974, 22000000, 189833357, 'Scott Calvin is an ordinary man, who accidentally causes Santa Claus to fall from his roof on Christmas Eve and is knocked unconscious. When he and his young son finish Santa''s trip and deliveries, they go to the North Pole, where Scott learns he must become the new Santa and convince those he loves that he is indeed, Father Christmas.', '/rcQZmnhcb6P4mkgJAHnCYp3c1gp.jpg', '/hrZjAYAF1o37k4Qb442c4yxwVLw.jpg', 0),
        (111127, 'Serial Mom', 1994, 10367, 7, 250, 13000000, 7820688, 'A picture perfect middle class family is shocked when they find out that one of their neighbors is receiving obscene phone calls. The mom takes slights against her family very personally, and it turns out she is indeed the one harassing the neighbor. As other slights befall her beloved family, the body count begins to increase.', '/jsvdBHxbBWCDFobiAxEwmKCCk1T.jpg', '/rH1TpgzOuZcjf6SpNTVMLs9GZUm.jpg', 0),
        (111161, 'The Shawshank Redemption', 1994, 4027, 9, 13004, 25000000, 28341469, 'Framed in the 1940s for the double murder of his wife and her lover, upstanding banker Andy Dufresne begins a new life at the Shawshank prison, where he puts his accounting skills to work for an amoral warden. During his long stretch in prison, Dufresne comes to be admired by the other inmates -- including an older prisoner named Red -- for his integrity and unquenchable sense of hope.', '/j9XKiZrVeViAixVRzCta7h1VU9W.jpg', '/9O7gLzmreU0nGkIB6K3BsJbzvNv.jpg', 0),
        (111194, 'A Simple Twist of Fate', 1994, 33405, 6, 40, 0, 0, 'When Michael McCann is thrown over by the woman he loves, he becomes something of a misanthrope and a miser, spending all of his spare money on collectible gold coins. Living in the same town is an affluent family with two sons: John and Tanny. Tanny''s a wild boy, whom John cannot control, and one night he breaks into McCann''s house, and steals the gold and disappears, which nearly confirms McCann''s distrust of mankind. But then, a mysterious young woman dies in the snow outside McCann''s house, and her small daughter makes her way to McCann''s house and into McCann''s life and heart. He names her Matilda, and raises her, finding companionship and a new joy in life with his adopted daughter. But the secret of Matilda''s birth may tear them apart.', '/gthFA6LxDQxH5qH36agphtdK29p.jpg', '/lxbPaaVF5zdknuf04iTDwQej7GM.jpg', 0),
        (111252, 'Spanking the Monkey', 1994, 17883, 6, 37, 200000, 0, 'Bright young student Raymond Aibelli is forced to sidetrack an important medical internship because his mother, Susan, is recovering from a broken leg. When he isn''t tasked with the most mundane aspects of Susan''s recuperation, Raymond finds distraction in a neighborhood girl, Toni Peck. But, as Susan begins relying on her son for both physical and emotional needs, Raymond starts developing disturbing and unwanted new yearnings.', '/zu4NFqTbvaVHLzi1GdLZBbcTl1x.jpg', '/nr3KNkAu7tmiaBnNgxabrcyCLX0.jpg', 0),
        (111280, 'Star Trek: Generations', 1994, 2380, 7, 655, 38000000, 120000000, 'Captain Jean-Luc Picard and the crew of the Enterprise-D find themselves at odds with the renegade scientist Soran who is destroying entire star systems. Only one man can help Picard stop Soran''s scheme...and he''s been dead for seventy-eight years.', '/mmwQBfWmEqJBOwfsjIBJPchXlSP.jpg', '/wjrXjlNpDq9U8vYmAwf420yDFtn.jpg', 0),
