        (111333, 'The Swan Princess', 1994, 107274, 7, 497, 20000000, 9771658, 'The beautiful princess Odette is transformed into a swan by an evil sorcerer''s spell. Held captive at an enchanted lake, she befriends Jean-Bob the frog, Speed the turtle and Puffin the bird. Despite their struggle to keep the princess safe, these good-natured creatures can do nothing about the sorcerer''s spell, which can only be broken by a vow of everlasting love.', '/hP9dsGy8FR7eeTqzpOpP3tl3wFD.jpg', '/oYp2bckWNBKOIbznjAfypVoMOFl.jpg', 0),
