        (115438, '2 Days in the Valley', 1996, 27846, 6, 108, 0, 0, 'In a sleepy bedroom community of LA''s San Fernando Valley, the murder of a professional athlete by two hit men sets into motion a chain of events that puts the mundane lives of a dozen residents on a collision course. This clever tale tells the story of two hit men, a mistress, a nurse, a vindictive ex-wife, a wealthy art dealer and his lovelorn assistant, a suicidal writer and his dog, and a bitter cop and his partner.', '/g5u3wpzMSQ8ytPxBmU5Zuo2YLOE.jpg', '/fT4ELMHeGzrSk1x2guF6vImgtiy.jpg', 0),
