        (148668, 'Bill Hicks: Relentless', 1992, 108258, 9, 33, 0, 0, 'Outspoken and raw, not mincing matters, Bill Hicks tells us that, just like smokers, non-smokers also die every day - with jogging instructor Jim Fixx as an example -, asks women what''s so terrible about giving head, talks us through what really happened during the 1990-1991 Gulf War and how the used technology could have also been used to feed the poor of the world.', '/bcTuCGNOl0rgfAxNqCS4Nr13Zks.jpg', '/32lUxq4tk5M8FJPRgxPHTwFmbgn.jpg', 0),
