        (151582, 'The Minus Man', 1999, 583, 6, 30, 0, 370668, 'The Minus Man is a 1999 film based on the novel by Lew McCreary. It was directed by Hampton Fancher, who also wrote the screenplay. The film centers on a psychotic killer whom Fancher describes as "a cross between Psycho''s Norman Bates, Melville''s Billy Budd and Being There''s Chauncey Gardner"', '/ytWoGt7aLbWImU7WUg8DgNjwkc3.jpg', '/kYWiKvqpIOCj1AyKa8E60tsvRcj.jpg', 0),
