        (174480, 'Autumn in New York', 2000, 6720, 6, 298, 65000000, 0, 'Autumn in New York follows the sexual exploits of Will Keane - New York restaurateur, infamous verging-on-50 playboy, master of the no-commitment seduction - until he runs into an unexpected dead end when he meets Charlotte Fielding. Charlotte is half Will''s age and twice his match, a 21 year-old free spirit yearning to get out and taste the excitement of adult life.', '/zXsskYrKF8QSivBykfMp48AdtuM.jpg', '/tQ5ze794HtDjxTxYVxHRn7AzbSL.jpg', 0),
