        (211181, '102 Dalmatians', 2000, 15775, 5, 680, 85000000, 183611771, 'Get ready for a howling good time as an all new assortment of irresistible animal heroes are unleashed in this great family tail! In an unlikely alliance, the outrageous Waddlesworth... a parrot who thinks he''s a Rottweiler... teams up with Oddball... an un-marked Dalmation puppy eager to earn her spots! Together they embark on a laugh-packed quest to outwit the ever-scheming Cruella De Vil', '/2s1vbGNvXfVqWAh2rBed6bm763R.jpg', '/dSxnIika9yWwTvEbpsmoGdeh65E.jpg', 0),
