        (238112, 'Captain Corelli''s Mandolin', 2001, 18844, 6, 247, 57000000, 62112895, 'When a Greek fisherman leaves to fight with the Greek army during WWII, his fiancee falls in love with the local Italian commander. The film is based on a novel about an Italian soldier''s experiences during the Italian occupation of the Greek island of Cephalonia (Kefalonia), but Hollywood made it into a pure love story by removing much of the "unpleasant" stuff.', '/sZd49cgewKjLA3TAFXNF2nqJddC.jpg', '/kKDQgPvxf0hjjlnKPp3oGblDsZR.jpg', 0),
