        (239948, 'Saving Silverman', 2001, 17494, 5, 254, 22000000, 19351569, 'A pair of buddies conspire to save their best friend from marrying the wrong woman, a cold-hearted beauty who snatches him from them and breaks up their Neil Diamond cover band.', '/f2zhXVpX9SXb7M9uIppVvVaF4S7.jpg', '/8JFs7ENQqCwG0FF3S1z5IobY1oE.jpg', 0),
