        (242423, 'Dude, Where''s My Car?', 2000, 56591, 5, 921, 13000000, 73180723, 'Jesse and Chester, two bumbling stoners, wake up one morning from a night of partying and cannot remember where they parked their car. They encounter a variety of people while looking for it, including their angry girlfriends, an angry street gang, a transexual stripper, a cult of alien seeking fanatics, and aliens in human form looking for a mystical device that could save or destroy the world.', '/pnjx4qRWN3qQb9y65BvuGrnWXRZ.jpg', '/3KoZiWlgvmeDYiLk9oOMpEvZThb.jpg', 0),
