        (242587, 'L.I.E.', 2001, 84931, 7, 47, 700000, 1667192, 'In this biting and disturbing coming-of-age tale from writer-director Michael Cuesta, life is bittersweet along the L.I.E., also known as the Long Island Expressway, as suburban teen Howie Blitzer learns all too clearly. In the space of a week, he loses nearly everything and everyone he knows and is left to navigate his adolescence virtually unsupervised.', '/eANN3omWwt14HTLeCoubBL5karL.jpg', '/9IEEv9jxBrUYltfV0VURsv0fdcA.jpg', 0),
