        (244000, 'American Outlaws', 2001, 56911, 6, 97, 35000000, 13678913, 'When a Midwest town learns that a corrupt railroad baron has captured the deeds to their homesteads without their knowledge, a group of young ranchers join forces to take back what is rightfully theirs. They will become the object of the biggest manhunt in the history of the Old West and, as their fame grows, so will the legend of their leader, a young outlaw by the name of Jessie James.', '/3AK7QCIA9j2u5ux6zjF1eDfd1Mt.jpg', '/cijrhkluznw3T6ZAh2wDP5EUtOs.jpg', 0),
        (244244, 'Swordfish', 2001, 58498, 6, 1457, 102000000, 147080413, 'Rogue agent Gabriel Shear is determined to get his mitts on $9 billion stashed in a secret Drug Enforcement Administration account. He wants the cash to fight terrorism, but lacks the computer skills necessary to hack into the government mainframe. Enter Stanley Jobson, a n''er-do-well encryption expert who can log into anything.', '/9iUG3L5pJjfIJBaaCOl1ucdAM4e.jpg', '/uJdI3eau8BHgTsrUbAeccnKn0ez.jpg', 0),
