        (247425, 'In the Bedroom', 2001, 5010, 7, 146, 1700000, 0, 'Summertime on the coast of Maine, "In the Bedroom" centers on the inner dynamics of a family in transition. Matt Fowler is a doctor practicing in his native Maine and is married to New York born Ruth Fowler, a music teacher. His son is involved in a love affair with a local single mother. As the beauty of Maine''s brief and fleeting summer comes to an end, these characters find themselves in the midst of unimaginable tragedy.', '/kWa4iUaC7SU2DHDlknlVvw5x9nP.jpg', '/3UzsHGayLvoInQrgIKd4u2y9BeA.jpg', 0),
