        (313911, 'Agent Cody Banks', 2003, 21981, 5, 561, 28000000, 58795814, 'Recruited by the U.S. government to be a special agent, nerdy teenager Cody Banks must get closer to cute classmate Natalie in order to learn about an evil plan hatched by her father. But despite the agent persona, Cody struggles with teen angst.', '/rHuyKvgXGv59mzx70E3t5jzONxS.jpg', '/fhK0mqqirPsckxkNisvi32A4lf6.jpg', 0),
