        (337636, 'Hellraiser: Deader', 2005, 58209, 5, 118, 4000000, 0, 'In London, after investigating crack addicted junkies for an article in her newspaper, Amy Klein watches a bizarre videotape where an underground group of youngsters in Bucharest apparently becoming zombies. Amy finds Marla dead with a puzzle cube in her hands. She brings the object to her hotel room, and opens it, beginning her journey to hell.', '/rp8mjdN9NE081rg2M5nJmBVLkVL.jpg', '/9XhcdTGqIR8fbOAfe7UOELvvglT.jpg', 0),
