        (387808, 'Idiocracy', 2006, 17403, 6, 1270, 30000000, 495303, 'To test its top-secret Human Hibernation Project, the Pentagon picks the most average Americans it can find - an Army private and a prostitute - and sends them to the year 2505 after a series of freak events. But when they arrive, they find a civilization so dumbed-down that they''re the smartest people around.', '/crwNKUOVf24JdNbPdVAZVbt6q9X.jpg', '/fPAhLmWdXDuwDPb37ccc6DqkJiw.jpg', 0),
